Package gw.api.tools

Class MBeansData

java.lang.Object
gw.api.tools.MBeansData
public class MBeansData extends Object
This class contains methods for dealing with MBeans. It may perform operations on MBeans and capture the result of those operations so object of this type are NOT THREAD SAFE. Note that just instantiating the GWMBean, is not sufficient for it to be picked up by the management agent, it most be registered via @link gw.api.tools.MBeansData#registerBean(gw.plugin.management.GWMBean)

    • getBeanOperationResult

      public Object getBeanOperationResult(OperationInfo opInfo)
      Return the captured result from an operation. @see gw.api.tools.MBeansData#executeBeanOperation(gw.plugin.management.GWMBean, java.lang.String) This is the same result returned via @see gw.api.tools.MBeansData#executeBeanOperation(gw.plugin.management.GWMBean, gw.plugin.management.OperationInfo). The operation must have been executed by this instance of MBeansData. This is not thread safe, is thread dependent.
      Parameters:
      opInfo - the operation whose result you want
      Returns:
      the result
